      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Organizers</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-funded-by field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who paid for the project or initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">University of Pennsylvania</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-funding-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Funding Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_funding_entity_kind%3A26">Academic Institution</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-organization field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who was primarily responsible for organizing the initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-implementing-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Organizing Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_implementing_entity_kind%3A26">Academic Institution</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-org-entity-other field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Other: Organizing Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Penn Project for Civic Engagement</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-initiative-support-other field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who else supported the initiative? :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">City of Philadelphia, WHYY</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Types of Supporting Entities:&n